Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新~年~快~樂~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薺 照妳這麼慢吞吞的 年早就過完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年賀卡必須要在元旦前夕投出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後對方第二天收到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖…雖然很難辦到…但是新學期開始前應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 小薺怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著說著就把說的話寫上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能趕在開學前寫完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}郵戳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我想親手做圖章的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…那個還未使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著做了一點點 馬上就受打擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沒注意到已經刻好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這個「祝」字 好像沒什麼年味兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著蓋一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 小薺有這麼大的暖被爐真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思哇 不經意間我們就都聚過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡 是家裡用的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 現在是蜜柑猜謎時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在袋子裡有三個蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該產品的農家…山內先生的興趣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我們怎麼知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃妳搶答了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山內先生的興趣是跳傘運動…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來問題還有下文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 問題是他的興趣是否是跳傘運動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這三個蜜柑裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最甜的是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來嚐一嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起都給吃了怎麼分辨的出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋姐她們從補習班回來時已經是傍晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她們說了 大概6點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦 快過年了還補習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟距離考試也沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也有些許焦慮 些許壓力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 她二人在向陽莊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不怎麼把氣氛弄的熱熱鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是顧及到我們的感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那反過來我們去把氣氛搞的熱鬧一些怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是哪個都有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願沙英姐和尋姐能考試順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}「新年快樂 恭賀新禧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 萬一…要是名落孫山的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會繼續住在這裡複讀一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薺 說什麼晦氣話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也閃過一絲剛才的那個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把做好的寄出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…外面好冷哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 寄新年賀卡的時候順便去暖暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身子暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年前夜去泡澡堂 感覺好新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體的每一個地方都仔仔細細的洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能夠有個好心情去迎接新年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而將今年一年積攢的某種「東西」都洗去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然每天都有好好洗澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽小薺閣下一言 感觸頗深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也許是妳聽錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止 妳新年前夕都在哪裡度過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在老家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次像這樣度過新年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每年都是 只在新舊年交替的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家裡所有人都不在地球的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是辭歲迎新的那一瞬間跳起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學的時候我也玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家人…一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在支撐著這個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能順利寄出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 是房東姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夥都聚一起了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的正好 我正打算過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 新年慰問品 蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除夕夜的蕎麥麵啊 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年妳們是要在向陽莊過年的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房東姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也承蒙您多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客氣客氣 彼此彼此啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來年也請繼續眷顧向陽莊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然今天可以通宵玩了 但也僅限今天喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沙英姐和尋姐回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得 要裝得焦躁不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了 來看妳們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了 大家都在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 妳們吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和我們說的話 講給我們聽聽好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更讓她們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 我剛才不是都說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年的蕎麥麵來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是房東姐姐送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 看起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筷子弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日語中的「落とす」：指掉落 落下 也有落榜的意思 一般對應考生而言這句話比較忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小薺那可是禁語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了很多 想吃多少都可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得說是新年的蕎麥麵要是不吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,財運就會逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 剩下的就是慢悠悠的等過12點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說今天大家集體在這裡過年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃莉和小薺已經回過家了來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們倆都是聖誕節之後回去的 很快就又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說沙英姐和尋姐的補習班新年能放三天假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就想著大家要在一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面裡放的辣椒現在起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由乃嗎 我想看看妳那怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？大家現在剛剛吃完過年的蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我啦…是喵太他說的 由乃今天不回家 好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 喵太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧？牠一直都叫個不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他爸 誰讓妳隨便就給由乃打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…喵太打來的電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經能聽到除夕的鐘聲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 今年就要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪還在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成積雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 地面都凍上了 滑滑的讓人頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:40.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日語中的「滑る」：滑 滑行 但同時也有落榜的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼在意我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 反而讓我們很困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得好熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是很累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫醒她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 已經倒計時了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7 6 5 4 3 2 1！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次半夜來做新年參拜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 由乃姐很自然的抱著的那個 什麼時候買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不倒翁嗎 就在剛剛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 不自覺的就看對上眼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的眼睛還沒畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日本的不倒翁眼睛都需要自己來畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽籤的事怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等大家一起來的時候再抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薺 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尋姐打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 尋姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃？妳們現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起到神社來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我很擔心的啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們丟下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 我看妳們兩人都睡得那麼香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼…騙妳的啦 我們現在趕去妳們那邊可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們等著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英姐和尋姐醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說是這就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 那邊在分紅豆年糕湯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 不錯的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去要點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道好香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心頭暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 善哉 善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是這年糕湯的本意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「紅豆年糕湯」寫成漢字也能讀成「善哉」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃莉醬好博學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是昨天電視裡播過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼 年糕湯很好喝啊 善哉善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善哉 善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰怎麼看都不會膩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什麼時候雪就不下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有多少積雪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英姐 尋姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡的還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經先一步參拜結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊還在分發紅豆年糕湯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋 我們也去參拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英許了什麼願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？考試的事之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掛在哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的機會 和大家掛在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 由乃妳們在牌子上寫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掛在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們放到哪了來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經被埋到裡面去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起數1 2一起打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好緊張 去年我是抽到「大吉」來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的是「末吉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「運氣漸漸上升 心想必會事成」這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是中吉 寫著「安心讀書吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣暫時也就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是「末吉」 寫著安產無憂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是「小吉」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「超吉」！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「超吉」？我還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮 今年也是「超吉」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這麼強運啊 由乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽…抽到「大凶」了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃 不要沮喪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大凶也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「運氣不會再走低了 從今開始只會越來越好」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大凶」可不是那麼容易抽到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃 妳中大獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃姐 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能得到神明大人的眷顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把籤子結到神木那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今年能有好事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽泣 抽泣 抽泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位同學 恭賀新禧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師您這是怎麼了 新年伊始的抽泣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 這抽籤…今年又抽了「凶」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 我抽到了比老師還要糟糕的「大凶」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…由乃同學妳也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年伊始 還真是不走運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說 把這個籤結到舌尖上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有好事發生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:58.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}合格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:16:59.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:16:59.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沙英 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:00.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}祈願考試通過 沙英 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}祈願合格 絕對能合格！沙英 希望能順利通過 尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英！來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這個祈願牌 是剛剛供上去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許人還在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在那邊吃紅豆年糕湯邊等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去找找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…沒事啦 找不找都無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我現在是和大夥兒一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定還能給她新年的問候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既…既然都說到這份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去神社轉一圈看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這不是小由乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 房東姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 恭賀新禧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房東妳好 祝妳新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 這不是老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來這些孩子都承蒙您的教誨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也請嚴格的教導她們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房東姐姐 妳喝醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 要迎接新年 大夥要我過去一起搓麻將嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏得個滿堂紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年伊始 我還真是走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿堂紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的話 能看到元旦的日出喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然難得來一次 我們就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在這個地方見面了 真…真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝…祝妳新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 新年快樂 今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不介意的話 就在這裡和我們一起看元旦日出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目姐姐 新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 一年一度神聖的拂曉之時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常言道「一年之計在於春」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是「萬事開頭最關鍵」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年級的同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能當女子高中生的歲月也已經不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不留遺憾的瀟灑一回喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回到同學那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學 那我們再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目 考試…我們彼此都要加油努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用妳說人家也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我去新年聚會裡露個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由乃妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多已經困了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟一直都沒睡過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我們也回去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薺 小嘴巴張的好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃莉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 燴年糕 就等大家睡飽了之後再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的 我要吃三個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝好夢~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年第一次泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今年…也將是三年級生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…也是應試生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要像沙英姐尋姐那樣 找到自己奮鬥的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也會煩惱 失落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有能在一起分憂 一起努力的向陽莊的夥伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我 還有大家 能有個美好的新的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:09.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,12月31日~1月1日 完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:20.61,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,吸い込まれそうなくらい 晴れ晴れした朝の陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.92,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,目覚ましのベル鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.75,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,降り注ぐ光り受けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:34.80,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,心の境界線を さあ今日も飛び越えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.93,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行機雲 空に舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:45.44,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,描いてる 旅の途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:52.72,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,思い出は 続いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:58.13,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,待ち合わせはまだ先へ まだまだ見えない向こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.69,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ルールは無い 自由に放つキャンバス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:09.05,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,心と体のバランス 天秤の上で揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:14.37,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しい絵を連れてどんな夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:24.07,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今の この場所は 未来へ　繋がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:35.67,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,探して 夢ぐも どこにあるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:20.61,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,炫目到奪人心魄的璀璨朝陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.92,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧鐘的鈴聲悄然響起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.75,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴著傾注而下的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:34.80,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 今天也一起躍過心中的境界線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.93,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,飛機尾跡在空中飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:45.44,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,細心描繪 旅途中的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:52.72,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,留下回憶 永遠不會中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:58.13,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,約定的時刻尚在未來 在那模糊不清的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.69,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,無拘無束自由綻放的畫布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:09.05,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈與身體的平衡 在天枰上搖擺不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:14.37,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,帶上嶄新的繪畫 又將夢見怎樣的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:24.07,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個地方 與未來相連
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:35.67,OP-CH,NTP,0,0,0,,一直尋找的夢中雲彩 究竟位於何處呢
